                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6191" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1562</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8734 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风起再扬帆—联想服务数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Road of Digital Transformation of Lenovo Service</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马郑玮，王辉武，魏春霞，白晓晶，王梦涛，李鹏飞，齐明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">联想（北京）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">联想；智慧魔方系统；信息管理；数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Lenovo; “Rubik’sCube”intelligent System; Information Management; Digital Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为全球PC行业的龙头企业，联想（北京）有限公司致力于满足顾客需求，解决顾客问题，提高顾客对产品的满意度，始终将服务质量与用户体验放在首位，在众多同类行业品牌中赢得用户信赖。本案例以联想智慧服务数字化转型与发展为主线，回顾联想服务1.0和2.0再到现今以联想魔方系统为代表的智慧服务时代发展历程。通过探讨联想智慧服务数字化转型的内外部动因，决策过程及转型过程中技术方案选择的依据，发现数字化转型进入智慧服务解决方案的路径与方法，全方位多角度地为我国服务行业的数字化发展提供启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous progress of social science and technology and the continuous upgrading of information, digitalization and consumer services, the existing customer service system of enterprises is also facing a severe test. A new generation of digital customer service system with high efficiency, flexibility, security and stability, cost control, big data, cloud computing and artificial intelligence is becoming the first choice of more and more enterprises. As a leading enterprise in the global PC industry, Lenovo ( Beijing ) Co., Ltd. is committed to meeting customer needs, solving customer problems, and improving customer satisfaction with products. It has always put service quality and user experience in the first place, and won user trust in many brands of similar industries. This case takes the digital transformation and development of Lenovo &#39; s smart service as the main line, and reviews the development process of Lenovo &#39; s 1.0 and 2.0 to the current era of smart service. By discussing the internal and external causes of Lenovo &#39;s digital transformation of smart services, the decision-making process and the basis for the selection of technical solutions in the transformation process, it is found that the path and method of digital transformation into smart service solutions provide enlightenment for the digital development of China &#39;s service industry from all aspects and angles.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》，《管理信息系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
